results.title: Pariah
results.description: Brief Daredevil Origin; Turk dressed as Santa knifes Matt in the gut; Ben is warned off of investigating a story about Murdock and the Kingpin; A wounded Matt is tended by Sister Maggie.

Daredevil by Frank Miller & Klaus Janson (Hardcover)

results.title: DD Goes Wild
results.description: The Marauder transports DD and Gladiator back to his base in hopes of using Hornhead to help power his Tri-Man; When this plan fails, he transports them both to a movie set of the Roman Coliseum in Europe where all the Maggia heads are meeting; DD and Gladiator fight it out in the arena until a caged lion gets loose and DD ends up saving his foe's life; Gladiator refuses to fight after this and gets a job with the Maggia; DD walks away.

results.title: Born Again
results.description: Daredevil is nursed back to health by Sister Maggie; Karen makes It to New York looking for Matt; Ben tries to come to grips with his story on Murdock and Kingpin; Kingpin commissions a Daredevil costume from Melvin Potter; Matt finds out that Sister Maggie is his mother.

results.title: Saved
results.description: Ben begins his expose on the Kingpin and his wife is almost killed for his efforts; Matt fights the Kingpin's goon in a Daredevil costume and takes the costume after the battle; Matt and Karen are re-united.

results.description: Matt helps Karen kick her drug habit; Kingpin hires a deranged Super Soldier to go after DD.

results.title: Armageddon
results.description: Captain America intervenes in Daredevil's battle with Nuke and finds out that the government has still been using the Super Soldier Program; Cap and DD link Kingpin with the Nuke fiasco and ruin his rep.

results.title: American Dreamer
results.description: DD and the Widow track down another deranged member of the Super Soldier Project.

results.title: The Mystery of the Midnight Stalker
results.description: DD makes his way to England where he finds that Ka-Zar is accused of being the Midnight Stalker; DD realizes that The Plunderer is trying to frame his brother, and the dynamic duo track him down; In a last panel shocker, Karen opens a letter to Matt from Spider-Man stating that the Web-Slinger knows that he and DD are one and the same.

results.title: Black Christmas
results.description: The Trixter leads DD on a merry Christmas chase.

results.title: A Cage In Search of a Bird
results.description: Karen convinces Matt to open a free legal hotline; Foggy is working for a big company run by the Kingpin; DD tries to investigate a company whose toxic waste blinded a little boy; Wolverine is on the trail of the mutant killing Bushwacker

results.title: Kiss and Kill
results.description: Daredevil and Wolvie clash over their methods of bringing in the mutant killing Bushwacker.

results.title: Enter:  The Leap-Frog
results.description: In a moment of panic to protect his secret identity, Matt tells Foggy and Karen that DD is really his twin brother, Mike; So of course they want to meet him; And they do; Oh, and Leap-Frog hops into town as well.

results.title: Can Even DD Halt the Rampage of Bullet?
Ground Zero
results.description: New York is in a blackout due to the assault by Apocalypse's Horsemen, and DD and crew have to keep Ammo and his gang away from the ordinance they are trying to steal.

results.title: Merry Christmas, Kingpin!
results.description: DD and Kingpin spend Christmas in their own particular idioms.

results.title: Stilt-Man Strikes Again
results.description: Matt continues in his role as Mike Murdock, Daredevil supreme; The Leap-Frog hops away from his trial and when DD goes after him, he runs across Stilt-Man; The Masked Marauder searches for DD's secret identity and rescues Stilt-Man from Hornhead.

results.title: The Final Triumph of Typhoid Mary !
Vital Signs
results.description: DD's rogues gallery beats the stuffing out of him just in time for Typhoid to drop him off of a bridge.

results.title: Meltdown
results.description: The Torch searches for a dying Daredevil.

results.title: ...I Found Me In A Gloomy Wood Astray...
In Bitterness Not Far From Death...
Mike Murdock Must Die
results.description: The Marauder kidnaps Foggy, Karen and Matt to force them to reveal DD's secret ID; While a blazing battle takes place aboard the Marauder's helicopter, Spidey runs up against Stilt-Man.
